These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, traveling, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, entrepreneur, project-manager, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, pop, blues
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 3. the fan pop is not to the right of the fan jazz##8
 4. the fan jazz is not to the left of the electrician##8
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan pop##1
 7. the scientist is the fan salsa##1
 8. the fan pop is not the electrician##6
 9. the fan jazz is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the project-manager##8
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
12. the fan jazz is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the entrepreneur##2
13. the fan pop and the project-manager have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | filmmaking      | puzzles | sudoku |
| Job           | project-manager | electrician | entrepreneur      | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | pop        | jazz            | blues    | salsa |

