.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, folk, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, ice-hockey, skiing
 1. the fan folk is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 3. the person who's sport is basketball and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
 4. the fan folk is somewhere to the right of the fan punk##5
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the fan punk is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan trance##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the fan punk##1
11. the fan dubstep is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the fan punk is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
13. the fan punk is on the left of the fan folk##1
14. the fan folk is not to the left of the person drinking water##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate   | lemonade     | water     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | dubstep   | punk      | folk    |
| Sport         | skiing   | basketball | ice-hockey | water-polo |

