.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, rock-climbing, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, spanish, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: horse, frog, goat, cat
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the brazilian##8
 2. the spanish is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the spanish is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere between the nigerian and the owner of the frog##7
 5. the person who's hobby is chess and the brazilian have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
 8. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the brazilian##1
10. the owner of the horse is between the brazilian and the owner of the cat##2
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the brazilian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | chess | rock-climbing     | camping  | card-games |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | brazilian    | spanish | nigerian |
| Pet           | goat       | frog | horse     | cat  |

