.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, hot-chocolate, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, singing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, tennis, surfing, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is singing have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is card-games have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola  | juice        | hot-chocolate  | tea |
| Hobby      | card-games  | collecting    | singing | skydiving |
| Sport      | surfing | parkour | weightlifting | tennis    |

