There 4 different types of food: potato, papaya, pomegranate, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, scooter, boat, bike
 1. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 2. the person eating potato and the person drinking sprite have different parity positions##9
 3. the person driving the bike is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 6. the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating pomegranate have different parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person eating potato and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
10. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk | sprite      | 7up        |
| Food        | pomegranate  | potato       | orange     | papaya  |
| Transport   | bike      | boat        | scooter | trike |

